        <li>Vintage: How recent are field data?</li>
        <li>Transparency: From what sources do field data come?</li>
        </ul>
        <li>Consistency and completeness</li>
        <ul>
        <li>OPGEE primary parameters (steam-to-oil ratio, API gravity, water-to-oil ratio): How many primary parameters are included in inputs?</li>
        <li>OPGEE secondary parameters (field depth, productivity index, number of wells, production rate): How many secondary parameters are included in inputs?</li>
        <li>Availability of flaring data: Are data available from satellite imagery and reporting?</li>
        </ul>
        </ul>
        <p>PRELIM:</p>
